import React from 'react' import './css/BusLogs.css' function BusLogs ({ buses, dates, sendDate }) { return (
{buses.forEach(bus => { return (

{bus.from.toUpperCase()}

{bus.to.toUpperCase()}

{sendDate}

{bus.time}

{bus.remaining} seats available

{bus.totalSeats} total seates.

) })}
) } export default BusLogs
